//------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// 2.7.0 | 2021-07-06 | mmcc | STRY0102408 Task Tree Manager tool tip displays Unicode Decimal Codes when entering 
//												some special characters in "instruction" or "Signature Instructions" field
//											Instructions and Signature Instructions need HTML converted to string before
//											the call to substring with field.maxChars;
//											Update .href to use dot notation for state and order
//											Combined Template Widget Data into here;
// 2.7.0 | 2021-11-16 | raj  | STRY0113839 - Technical Story: Pages/Portal/Page should be picked up from the "Form preferences"
//											NOTE: href was no longer used.  So, removed completely to avoid future confusion
// 2.7.3 | 2022-05-04 | raj |  DFCT0010902 - When a template task record is updated the Template Task Number in the node text is set to null.
//                                           This is cleared with the next refresh
// 2.8 | 2022-03-04 | mmcc | STRY0114453 - Org Hierarchy Full Screen- Tree Node- Avatar Control- Popover Panel
//											Updated loadPhotoInfo() to use sys_user; Added getConnectEnabled();
//											in loadProfileInfo() added mobilePhone, contactPageHref, photo, emailSubject, buttonText and icons;
//											Changed phone to businessPhone
// 2.8 | 2022-03-10 | mmcc | STRY0114453 - Org Hierarchy Full Screen- Tree Node- Avatar Control- Popover Panel
//											Cleaned up getConnectEnabled(); Added object pages; 
//											Removed emailSubject and buttonText as they will added to the pages object
// 2.8 | 2022-03-24 | mmcc | STRY0115677 - Org Hierarchy Full Screen- Process Request Indicator- Popover Styling
//											loadProfileInfo() var userProfile deleted unused fields
//											_setStyleBackgroundImage(photo) as calling with 2nd param asBackgroundImage
//  2.8   - 2022-08-16 - raj - DFCT0011078 - Long Task name should NOT impact the  "Task Name", "state" and  "user" name in the Task Tree View
//  2.8   - 2022-08-20 - raj - DFCT0011140 - Record watcher: "Warning Icon" &  "Duration icon"  should NOT trigger the visual warning indicator on load. (Taker Type "Approval)
//  2.8   - 2022-08-26 - raj - STRY0128070 - Existing Task Form- All Content Tabs- "New" Button displays next to Header
// 
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

